Global Favipiravir Tablets Market Insights
Favipiravir Tablets Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Favipiravir Tablets Market Overview
The global Favipiravir tablets market is expected to grow significantly, with a projected market value of USD 3.5 billion by 2030, driven by the increasing demand for antiviral treatments, particularly during global health crises. Favipiravir is widely used for treating influenza and COVID-19, contributing to its growing market demand. As the world continues to face infectious disease outbreaks, the need for effective antiviral treatments is becoming more critical. Additionally, the expanding pharmaceutical pipeline and ongoing clinical trials for additional indications will drive the market's future growth.

